    "description": "各位角斗士！欢迎来到充满血腥的战场。这里可没人玩石头剪刀布，挺着火枪拉大栓更管用！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801750/extras/1a5afd9f76e3626206b7c82cda21d83d.avif?t=1727940601\" width=616 height=616 /></span><br><br>《Hot Shot Burn》是一款疯狂无限制的俯视角派对厮杀游戏。来自宇宙不同角落的太空角斗士将在最受欢迎的直播擂台展开厮杀。支持最多4位玩家，可在线或本地游戏。玩家可体验到疯狂、血腥、无视物理定律的战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801750/extras/7da8bdc231c20918866c3b26f11fc3c5.poster.avif?t=1727940601\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801750/extras/7da8bdc231c20918866c3b26f11fc3c5.webm?t=1727940601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801750/extras/7da8bdc231c20918866c3b26f11fc3c5.mp4?t=1727940601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>多个英雄供你选择，包括放荡不羁的太空摔跤手、致命的杀手飞蛾、毛茸茸不知所措的外星生物。每个角色都有独特的风格与技能。找到你中意的角色，与好友激战到底，让观众沸腾。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801750/extras/b8b06e7d81b8416f15ca81092bc26a71.avif?t=1727940601\" width=616 height=184 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>适合2-4位玩家的快节奏多人动作游戏，充满不可预知的元素。<br></li><li>支持本地及在线游戏！<br></li><li>多个含独特危险要素及规则的战场。<br></li><li>能扭曲现实、改变战局的突变器。<br></li><li>受周末卡通片启发的艺术风格。<br></li><li>火爆的合成器音乐！</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >激烈的星际大厮杀！</h2>开播时间到了！在现场观众面前上演究极角斗士之战。观众热血沸腾！解说员拿你紧身裤开玩笑！大家都很HIGH！（当然指活着的人……）<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801750/extras/ac7f2afa08a4518a30fdd7153d714283.poster.avif?t=1727940601\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801750/extras/ac7f2afa08a4518a30fdd7153d714283.webm?t=1727940601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801750/extras/ac7f2afa08a4518a30fdd7153d714283.mp4?t=1727940601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不择手段！</h2>你们来这儿就是为赢得比赛的，谁还会去在乎“公平竞赛”或“物理原理”？瞬移、隐身、用墙反弹子弹、穿墙射击……不择手段，只为挺到最后。在太空角斗场，一切都是“公平”的。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801750/extras/56abc58992269cb5018807c61e52f947.poster.avif?t=1727940601\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801750/extras/56abc58992269cb5018807c61e52f947.webm?t=1727940601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/801750/extras/56abc58992269cb5018807c61e52f947.mp4?t=1727940601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
